metadata.name: PEPE warrior and dragon egg
metadata.description: pepe warriors There must be a companion animal for each person. which must be raised since they are still in the egg So you will get a partner who knows your heart and understands each other. and JK. when the youngest of the pepe warriors I want a dragon to become my body's companion. The pepe warriors came to help. Which will have to adventure with many dangers before getting a dragon egg to raise a partner
